A state of adding new functionality
===================================
Streaming of nature is not independent in its streaming, there are many atoms/molecule/wave/intensity of particular state of energy/atmosphere/temperature..so on
stream inside it.

The internal streaming is nothing but for the support of external streaming of any object. Streaming of object is not only depends on the internal streaming but the 
external atmosphere together.

***Internal streaming is just the base/support of external streaming of object***

Ex-
If you are in software development field and you develop a software, you can observe there are chain of support for your development internally and your requirement is nothing but
the external service of human being.

Your application need support of tomcat,JDK(java development kit that support to execute your application).
The jdk,tomcat need operating system to execute it, operating system need cpu, cpu need register, register need particular type of wire..etc
You may observe to develop an software application for serve human being how many revolution phase completed in hardware/software.

If you are a farmer,
If you want to grow some plant, you need to know the sate of soil that support the fertilization.
In process of fertilization the soil already took many revolution.
It depends up on farmer knowledge what they want to grow and what soil support.

Similar way life have taken many revolution to come in current state.
All of our physical activity are directly supported by internal process/execution in body/mind/intellect..so on.

Whatever we build in our life is just an application to run our life smoothly.
Whatever we build is not sudden build but time to time we add new functionality in our life.
Ex-
We join a job,We take house, We take car, We make relationship, We make friend, We marry,We start business..etc these are the new functionality that we add time to time.
Due to adding new functionality every time we become a large application.

If we add new functionality in our life without proper analysis(lack of knowledge/poor understanding) and development , the same functionality arise bug for our life.
Whatever bug in your life that need to solve by you only since you have added new functionality and no one know how did you analysis and develop before use it.

Every one is crazy to add new functionality in their life without proper knowledge/analysis/development, and due to poor knowledge/analysis/development
lot of bug arise during use of it. These bug is nothing but the stress during running our application/life.

***Your inner execution of energy is just to support your external application/life***

It is completely your responsibility, how to develop your life/application/adding new functionality so it can run without any bug.

***Bug of life is nothing but the stress during running our life/application***
***Your life/application had developed by you only that you run every moment of your life***
 
